  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Sonic returns to the DS with all the classic 2D dual screen action of \"Sonic Rush,\" as well as a new high-seas adventure where he clashes with ruthless pirates. As Sonic, set off from Windmill Village to explore seven islands for action-packed adventures spread across a large map. As you venture, you'll uncover valuable items and materials that will help Tails build new ships so that Sonic can track down the villainous pirates in a variety of ways.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
